# Draft:People's Republic of Shkumbin

People's Republic of Shkumbin (PRS) Albanian: Republika Popullore e Shkumbinit (RPS) is a micronation establishment by First secretary Antolin in 22 June 2024 and 2 days later on 24 June 2024 established the People's Strategical Defense Force (PSDF) Albanian:Forca e Mbrojtjes Strategjike Popullore (FMSP)
